update.name: Cordless 7 Speed Hand Mixer (Charco al Gray)
update.description:
Cordless 7 Speed
Hand Mixer All the Power You Expect, without the Cord. Go where ambition takes you with the Cordless Hand Mixer from KitchenAid. Designed with a powerful rechargeable Lithium Ion Battery, the new cordless hand mixer delivers optimal run time and performance, so you can cook wherever*, whatever, and however you choose. Make up to 200 cookies on a full charge.** *Indoor use only. **Based on 4 batches of chocolate chip cookies.
update.short_description:
5G speed. A14 Bionic, the fastest chip in a smartphone. An edge-to-edge OLED display. Ceramic Shield with four times better drop performance.
  • 6.1-inch Super Retina XDR display2
  • Ceramic Shield, tougher than any smartphone glass
  • 5G for superfast downloads and high-quality streaming
[motta_more] All the Power You Expect, without the Cord. Go where ambition takes you with the Cordless Hand Mixer from KitchenAid. [/motta_more]
